review.description: veggie dishes that leave you feeling full and satisfied. kale n' sweet potato, curried grilled veggies, chilis and lentils. best home made raisin bread i've ever had.  overall: simple in a good way, perfectly seasoned, and great value. oh and it's in the basement if a Hindu temple! So, you know, cool hipster bragging rights there...
review.author: Joe S.
